---
const year = new Date().getFullYear()
---
<footer style="background: #0D1B3E; border-top: 1px solid rgba(29,184,232,0.15); margin-top: 4rem;">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-10">

      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <a href="/blog" style="text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 4px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 12px;">
          <span style="font-family: 'Sora', system-ui, sans-serif; font-weight: 900; font-size: 1.4rem; color: #1DB8E8; letter-spacing: -0.02em;">ZEN</span>
          <span style="font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; font-style: italic; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff; font-size: 1rem;">caps</span>
          <span style="color: #6B7A9A; font-size: 0.65rem; margin-left: 8px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; align-self: center;">Blog</span>
        </a>
        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7A9A; line-height: 1.7; font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;">
          Conteúdo baseado em ciência sobre sono, ansiedade e bem-estar natural.
        </p>
        <!-- Social links -->
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 12px; margin-top: 16px;">
          <a
            href="https://www.instagram.com/zencapsoficial/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Instagram Zen Caps"
            style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(29,184,232,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(29,184,232,0.2); color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;"
            onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(29,184,232,0.18)'; this.style.borderColor='#1DB8E8'; this.style.color='#1DB8E8'"
            onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(29,184,232,0.08)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(29,184,232,0.2)'; this.style.color='#6B7A9A'"
          >
            <!-- Instagram icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <rect x="2" y="2" width="20" height="20" rx="5" ry="5"></rect>
              <path d="M16 11.37A4 4 0 1 1 12.63 8 4 4 0 0 1 16 11.37z"></path>
              <line x1="17.5" y1="6.5" x2="17.51" y2="6.5"></line>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://www.facebook.com/zencapsoficial"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            aria-label="Facebook Zen Caps"
            style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; width: 36px; height: 36px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(29,184,232,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(29,184,232,0.2); color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.2s;"
            onmouseover="this.style.background='rgba(29,184,232,0.18)'; this.style.borderColor='#1DB8E8'; this.style.color='#1DB8E8'"
            onmouseout="this.style.background='rgba(29,184,232,0.08)'; this.style.borderColor='rgba(29,184,232,0.2)'; this.style.color='#6B7A9A'"
          >
            <!-- Facebook icon -->
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 0 0-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        <!-- Glow line -->
        <div style="height: 2px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #1DB8E8 0%, transparent 100%); border-radius: 4px; margin-top: 16px; width: 60px; opacity: 0.6;"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Categories -->
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Sora', system-ui, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: 14px; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">
          Categorias
        </h3>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;">
          <li>
            <a href="/blog/categoria/sono" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; transition: color 0.15s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#1DB8E8'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6B7A9A'">
              Sono &amp; Insônia
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/blog/categoria/ansiedade" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; transition: color 0.15s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#1DB8E8'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6B7A9A'">
              Ansiedade &amp; Estresse
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/blog/categoria/ingredientes" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; transition: color 0.15s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#1DB8E8'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6B7A9A'">
              Ingredientes &amp; Ciência
            </a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <a href="/blog/categoria/habitos" style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif; transition: color 0.15s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#1DB8E8'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6B7A9A'">
              Hábitos Saudáveis
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-family: 'Sora', system-ui, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9); margin-bottom: 14px; font-size: 0.8rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em;">
          O Produto
        </h3>
        <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: #6B7A9A; margin-bottom: 20px; line-height: 1.7; font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;">
          Zen Caps é o suplemento natural com melatonina, triptofano e magnésio para você dormir melhor e controlar a ansiedade.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://zencaps.com.br"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="zen-btn-gold"
          style="font-size: 0.85rem;"
        >
          Conhecer o Zen Caps &rarr;
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom bar -->
    <div style="border-top: 1px solid rgba(29,184,232,0.1); padding-top: 24px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; align-items: center; text-align: center;">
      <div style="display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: center;">
        <a href="https://zencaps.com.br/politica-de-privacidade" style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#1DB8E8'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6B7A9A'">Política de Privacidade</a>
        <a href="https://zencaps.com.br/termos-de-uso" style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#1DB8E8'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6B7A9A'">Termos de Uso</a>
        <a href="https://zencaps.com.br" style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #6B7A9A; text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.15s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='#1DB8E8'" onmouseout="this.style.color='#6B7A9A'">Site Oficial</a>
      </div>
      <p style="font-size: 0.72rem; color: rgba(107,122,154,0.6); font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;">
        &copy; {year} Zen Caps. Todos os direitos reservados.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
